## 5. Session Routine

### At Session Start

```bash
# Check status
git status -sb
cat Plans.md
head -50 AGENTS.md
```

Or type "start session" to launch the skill.

### On Work Completion

```bash
# Commit (follow conventions)
git add -A
git commit -m "feat: [change description]"
git push

# Completion report
/handoff-to-cursor
```

